WEBVTT

00:10:31.068 --> 00:10:33.989
who you choose as
the other parent of your children.

00:10:35.137 --> 00:10:37.007
And of course, romance has to be there.

00:10:37.031 --> 00:10:41.226
Romance is a grand and beautiful
and quirky thing.

00:10:42.001 --> 00:10:47.418
But we need to add
to a romantic, loving heart

00:10:47.442 --> 00:10:51.588
an informed, thoughtful mind,

00:10:51.612 --> 00:10:54.597
as we make the most important
decision of our life.

00:10:54.621 --> 00:10:55.813
Thank you.

00:10:55.837 --> 00:10:59.575
(Applause)